The first of Morcar's sorcerous Lieutenants you must defeat is Zanrath, High Mage of Sarako.
He lives in a magical tower high in the Tarak Mountains, where he is guarded by his elite army
of Chaos Warriors. Prepare yourselves, my Heroes, for a fearsome battle against steel and magic.
</speech>
